Name: ISTJ
Description: Responsible organizers, driven to create order and apply standards. Detail-oriented and value loyalty and tradition.

Name: ISFJ
Description: Dedicated caretakers, eager to help and provide for others. Excel in practical care and support.

Name: INFJ
Description: Insightful visionaries, seeking meaning in relationships, ideas, and events. Aim to better the human condition.

Name: INTJ
Description: Strategic thinkers, determined to improve systems and processes. Innovative and insightful.

Name: ISTP
Description: Explorers of the physical world, adept at understanding how things work. Flexible problem solvers.

Name: ISFP
Description: Gentle caretakers, living in the moment and enjoying surroundings with quiet enthusiasm. Adaptable and sympathetic.

Name: INFP
Description: Idealistic dreamers, guided by core values and beliefs. Compassionate and creative.

Name: INTP
Description: Inventive thinkers, curious about the world. Seek to understand and improve.

Name: ESTP
Description: Energetic thrill-seekers, thrive on action. Pragmatic and straightforward problem solvers.

Name: ESFP
Description: Spontaneous entertainers, enjoying the spotlight and making others happy. Live in the moment and adept at sensing needs.

Name: ENFP
Description: Enthusiastic innovators, eager to explore new possibilities. Charismatic, imaginative, and value connections.

Name: ENTP
Description: Quick-witted debaters, seeing possibilities everywhere. Inventive and drawn to complexity.

Name: ESTJ
Description: Hardworking traditionalists, eager to organize. Practical, reliable, and value order and efficiency.

Name: ESFJ

Name: ENFJ
Description: Passionate leaders, skilled in communicating vision. Empathetic and organized.

Name: ENTJ
Description: Bold strategists, commanding and efficient. Drive to organize change and develop plans.

Name: Dominance-Influence

Name: Creative-Connector

Name: Guardian-Connector
